                           <q xml:lang="en">This (is) a Psalter which the father <persName ref="PRS12748Anonym"/> gave to
                             <persName ref="PRS11434KeflaDengel">Kǝfla Dǝngǝl</persName>, so that it might become salvation for
                             the flesh and soul, when (the date is) <date>the 19th year of mercy</date>. 10000 </q>
